pf.graph
Class EdgeImpl

java.lang.Object
  pf.graph.EdgeImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Edge
public class EdgeImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Edge

Default implementation of Edge.

Two edges are considered the same if the have the same end vertices, no matter of order.

There is nothing special here.

Author:
Adam Juraszek
